OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAfghanistan girls' tears   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fover chaotic Taliban       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fschools U-turn             
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Early this morning, at her home on a   
OL,6, hilltop in the west of Kabul,          
OL,7, 15-year-old Marzia packed her bag for  
OL,8, school, for the first time since the   
OL,9, Taliban took power last August.        
OL,11,F"I became so, so happy when I heard    
OL,12,Fschool was restarting," she told the   
OL,13,FBBC. "It makes me hopeful about the    
OL,14,Ffuture again."                         
OL,17,FSince August, in most of Afghanistan,  
OL,18,Fonly girls' primary schools have       
OL,19,Fremained open, along with all boys'    
OL,20,Fschools.                               
